{"tid":1536211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班白鳩痴唔想害死個十三歲細路，就咪撚再推個張相","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:36:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b69d8910818462bf57a996825e0ca7f6829c5f96","tid":1536211,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"（圖）呢個係咪13歲俾人告有汽油彈個個小朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">說好的fact check 呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n咁耐先有圖<br />\n仲要咁明顯咁完整影到<br />\n有埋汽油彈入鏡<br />\n咁啱後面乾淨冇路人接近冇背景<br />\n望落又冇煙<br />\n揸機又定，俾人影嗰個又定<br />\n但個日兵荒馬亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲要明知係藍絲group傳出嚟</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你9成事後補拍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係成個post頭8版冇人質疑可信性<br />\n全部人當真咁討論打丁<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嗰細路未判架<br />\n好可能俾差佬栽贜架<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街咁樣討論啲疑似偽造、對佢不利既證據<br />\n係咪想害撚死佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c79ef0a89a38501eb137674a73027e2fbdbfee2a","tid":1536211,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:05:2